thread.title_full: Plastek Cards reviewed by Nicolle Brown

author: Nicolle Brown
title: Nicolle Brown
text: This order ran pretty decently...a welcome change from my first order which was a nightmare of gargantuan proportion. I was pleased that everything ran as smoothly as it did in comparison. The time frame for the job ran a little longer than I would have liked, but overall it was a good experience. I will order from them again and I do hope, in the future, that I can recommend them to others.
